    "VESTIGE": "The mark of the foot left on the earth; a track or footstep; atrace; a sign; hence, a faint mark or visible sign left by somethingwhich is lost, or has perished, or is no longer present; remains; as,the vestiges of ancient magnificence in Palmyra; vestiges of formerpopulation.What vestiges of liberty or property have they left Burke.Ridicule has followed the vestiges of Truth, but never usurped herplace. Landor.",
