    "VESTMENT": "A covering or garment; some part of clothing or dress;specifically (Eccl.), any priestly garment. \"Royal vestiment.\"Chaucer. \"Priests in holy vestments.\" Shak.The sculptor could not give vestments suitable to the quality of thepersons represented. Dryden.",
