    "VIBRANT": "Vibrating; tremulous; resonant; as, vibrant drums. Longfellow.",
    "VIBRATILE": "Adapted to, or used in, vibratory motion; having the power ofvibrating; vibratory; as, the vibratile organs of insects.",
